<p class=""><em>indicated assent</em>.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-4ac3404c-0133-41ee-bd42-c1b4cace2965" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
