<p class="">Before the right hon. Gentleman proceeds would he make this clear to the House? Are we to understand that this question of the limitation to a 2d. rate was the sole point between his friends and the Secretary of State?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
