    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">What gas was used in those experiments?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-75655dff-ebb9-4823-b337-cefa2ac18d26" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
